text:
The text below is unwritten rules and information about the official contract for changing the ownership of the RTS bot

On "Tuesday, January 14, 2025 at 10:40:25 AM GMT+1" there was this change of ownership, which occurred in the time period "Tuesday, January 14, 2025 at 10:40:25 AM GMT+1 to Tuesday, January 14, 2025 at 10:40:25 AM GMT+1"

The change occurred on the basis of @DrMineword voluntarily relinquishing ownership of the RTS bot, without any exchange of any funds
RTS is now officially owned by "Anime Oni ðŸ§ª"
@DrMineword's powers have been reduced to shared management, development and advertising of the RTS bot
